These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dannemann, baccarat, montecristo
City: san-francisco, hamburg, venice, london
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, june, september
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the montecristo-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person traveling to hamburg##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's birthday is in june##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person traveling to hamburg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Cigar   | dannemann | montecristo   | ritmeester   | baccarat  |
| City         | hamburg  | venice  | london  | san-francisco |
| Birthday     | august    | june | november     | september    |

