.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, thai
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dannemann, bluemaster, siglo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia, daffodil, bellflower
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person who growszinnia and the dannemann-smoker##2
 2. the colombian is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
 3. the colombian is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the british is not to the right of the person who growsbellflower##8
 5. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the dannemann-smoker##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the thai##8
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
 9. the vegafina-smoker is the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
11. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##8
12. the thai is on the left of the colombian##1
13. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
15. the british is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the british is not to the right of the dannemann-smoker##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
19. the thai is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | british | dutch | thai  | colombian  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Cigar   | dannemann    | bluemaster  | siglo | vegafina |
| Flower           | daffodil | bellflower | zinnia    | begonia  |

