 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
 5. the thai is not to the right of the coach##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the dancer##8
 7. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
 8. the dancer is on the left of the engineer##1
 9. the engineer is on the left of the project-manager##1
10. the british is on the far right##1
11. the coach is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
12. the engineer is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
