The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person traveling to hannover is not the indonesian##6
 2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is the american##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is between the indonesian and the colombian##2
 5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 7. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the colombian is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
12. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
14. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
