There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, 7up, water
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, poker, mah-jongg
House: victorian, modern, art-deco, wooden
 1. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the modern house is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 4. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
 6. the art-deco house is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the modern house is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 8. the person playing billiard is the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
11. the wooden house is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person drinking cola##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the art-deco house##1
13. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
14. the modern house is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
