12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
13. the person traveling to prague is not to the left of the person eating blueberry##8
14. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person eating carrot##8
15. the person eating tomato is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Food           | artichoke | tomato       | blueberry      | carrot  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
| Pet   | fish   | horse          | hedgehog      | cat  |
| City   | london   | hamburg      | edinburgh | prague |

